title: Ticket.Of.No.Return.1979.TVRip.x264
description:
She, an unusually beautiful woman, has bought a one-way ticket to Berlin. She wanted to forget her past, or better still, to abandon it as if it were a condemned property. She wanted to direct all her energy into one thing, something that would belong exclusively to her. To follow her own destiny was, after all, her only wish. Berlin, a city in which she was a complete stranger, seemed like the ideal place to sate her longing. The time was right to put her plans into action.
